                    <li>tablespoon olive oil</li>
                    <li>1 pound lean ground beef</li>
                    <li>1/2 medium onion chopped</li>
                    <li>1 clove garlic minced</li>
                    <li>1.5 cups marinara sauce</li>
                    <li>Salt & pepper to taste</li>
                    <li>1.5 cups shredded cheddar cheese</li>
                </ul>
                <h6 class="card-subtitle mt-4 mb-2">Instructions:</h6>
                <ol>
                    <li>Preheat the oven to 375째F.</li>
                    <li>Cook the penne according to package instructions, then drain and set aside.</li>
