                    <li>Stir in the marinara sauce, salt, and pepper. Simmer for 5 minutes.</li>
                    <li>In a greased baking dish, layer half of the cooked penne, followed by half of the beef mixture, and half of the shredded cheddar cheese. Repeat the layers.</li>
