                    <li>Pour the mixture over the cod fillets, making sure they are evenly coated.</li>
                    <li>Bake for 15-20 minutes, or until the fish is cooked through and flakes easily with a fork.</li>
                    <li>Garnish with fresh parsley and serve immediately.</li>
